  1. Skogen
  ...
   I counted six sentences.
- Average number of words per sentence: (62/6) ≈ 10.33

Using the equation: 
LIX = (0.0188 × 4.45) + (0.0009 × (1/(62/6))) ≈ 0.08361+ 0.0009*1/(62/6)≈ 0.08361 + 0.137 ≈ 0.22061 

